        "path": "/books/kitab-al-duafa:5:3:1",
        "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/17/5/3/1",
        "text": [
          "3 - جعفر بن محمد بن مفضل، كوفي. يروي عنه الغلاة خاصة. وما رأيت له - قط - رواية صحيحة. وهو متهم في كل أحواله."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.tashayyu": [
            "3 – Jaʿfar b. Muḥammad b. Mufaḍḍal.  Kufan.  The ghulāt narrate from him exclusively.  I have never seen a single sound (ṣaḥīḥ) narration for him.  He was accused in all his aspects."
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
